Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't she just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I forgot to ask when the man would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was right. The silhouette {\i0}is{\i1} like a barrel or a balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to get a fake pin badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it suck if she couldn't find her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I figured I'd show her the badge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and make up a fake Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wanted to get her excited over nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two types of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies that hurt, and lies that don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think Suzuha would want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amane told me not to tell anyone this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that time machine can only travel backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you leave, you can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you brought me a refreshing Coke Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we fix the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You worked this whole time, but that's still amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru's the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to judge him by his looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he looks unhealthy and kind of dim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've changed my mind about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can help me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterward, in the steaming hot confines of the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we can forget our shame and take off our clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru and Suzu look good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm saying this because
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll ever have the chance to say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first came here, I didn't know anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though this era is much more peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow, to me, it was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I have lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy that I could come here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I could spend time with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I really had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could be a lab member,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,just for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once you leave, you can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe Rintarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the future—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to change the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it a free world like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe Rintarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you regret the memories you've made?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's time to say goodbye, do you think that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it would've been better if we'd never met?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida Itaru told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's worried about you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing the future was my father's wish—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't care what'll happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The '70s weren't {\i1}that{\i0} bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make friends like you there, \Nand I'll live freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's fine, but give it a final check.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be happier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You just fixed a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,1975...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what month and day I should go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What would be appropriate? "The Day of Great Luck"?{Taiankichijitsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or "the Day of Friends"?{Tomobiki, kanji for friend and pull}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Those days are for weddings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Day of Friends might be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It could help you make new friends faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends? That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,FG204?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my dad named the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it might fit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if we removed the tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii figured out who your dad is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's really close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I always felt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that you two made a great pair,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're father and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu's dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of this pervert getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't that a little mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you come to this conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,First, "barrel" means "taru," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru... Daru... Thus, Daru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But Okarin and Barrel Titor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,were also part of the group that founded the resistance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And in 2010's Akihabara, \Nthey were working on a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They even knew about Okarin's Reading Signer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That only leaves Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the most convincing piece of evidence Mayushii found was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,FG204.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a future gadget.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A future gadget?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's stuff to the right of it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Future Gadget 204,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,second edition, version 2.31"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That naming convention...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You should call me "daddy" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the time machine you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish what you started,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,was your mom cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a short one with a baby face and big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about Mayushii and the rest of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find the IBN 5100,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.00,op trans,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll get it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you in 35 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it'll only be a few hours for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.79,Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs18\frz336.5\frx28\fry358\pos(754,174)\fax-.05}Part-Time Soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.79,Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs23\frx14\fry2\fax-0.15\frz339\pos(707,182)}Thank You
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.79,Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs23\frx20\fry0\frz337.7\fax-0.15\pos(515,158)}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be sure we see each other again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep working hard until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so you try too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received word
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that the satellite that crashed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,into the Akihabara radio building has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think this pin badge \Ncould be our initials?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe's "O."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida's "H."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina's "S."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then "M" is for Makise, and "A" is for Amane, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A lab member badge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Divergence Meter hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it change after Amane brings us the IBN 5100 or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha's 54 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter's over 30 years older than I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be married with grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So at this age, I could see my own great-grandkids?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You should act grownup like a real great-grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Braun?
