Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.56,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz325.045\blur0.5\pos(440,696)}Okabe \NRintarou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.82,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs44\blur0.5\pos(408,488)\frz322.6}Hashida \NSuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that from Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a letter from someone who once took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked me to give it to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:00.25,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\b1\frz322.6\fs44\blur0.5\move(408,488,388,498,0,4319)\fad(0,1800)}Hashida \NSuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the great Okabe Rintarou,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's me, Amane Suzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may have only been a few hours to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but right now, it's June 13th, 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll get right to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only remembered who I was a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the past 24 years, I'd forgotten myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time travel didn't work correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The repair job was imperfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it wasn't my dad's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should've gone directly to 1975.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't have stopped in 2010.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't have been so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, the future won't change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't get an IBN 5100.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why have I even lived this long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I forgot my duty and squandered my life doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me! Forgive me! Forgive me! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.86,Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\an2\be2\fs40\t(500,2127,\fscy125\fscx125)\frz346\move(981,338,1301,346,500,2127)}Part-Time Soldier
