Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.86,Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\be2\an2\t(500,2127,\fscy125\fscx125)\move(458,408,636,436,500,2127)\frz346.3}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okabe Rintarou, when I tried to go to 1975,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}after the time machine forum meeting, \Nyou stopped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of the rain that night, \Nthe time machine broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you can go back in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ask that you not stop me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...was wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me how Hashida Suzu died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to know how she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how it happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't seem like simple curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's your relationship to Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,An old acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still remember
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,our time together very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She hanged herself in her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In the year before she died,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,she became mentally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But up until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,she was a cheerful, kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The time machine broke because
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped her back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd never sent that D-mail,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,she would've gone to 1975 right then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okabe, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate, Mayuri's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin, are you sending a D-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, all of this will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time we remember spending
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,with Suzu will have never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So please, change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard that name in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is she still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's been ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She really looked after me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've liked to have seen her at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she really commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She died of an illness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I live in her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she really loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So for ten years, I've kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, she and I were neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my house burned down in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and she let me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she alone that whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She never married...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, I asked her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,why she did all this for someone with no relationship to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She just laughed and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Everyone gets help
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,from someone else at some point in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So someday, you should help someone too."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One second...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu had this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the number means?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always looking at it from her hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She would say "Is this the number before it changes or after?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Did I manage to change it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever that meant, it bothered her to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The divergence number changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it hasn't gone past 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The train for the outer line will arrive shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Yamanote Line is working at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please stand behind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayushii's phone rang. Was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She was having a nice nap, so I didn't wake her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suzuha... did the world change?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has Mayuri been saved?
